    "details": {
      "description": "<p>This specialized wagon contains everything you need to ply your trade on the road. It counts as a suitable workshop and provides artisan’s tools for one type of crafting, even while moving. Additionally, you don’t take the penalty for making a downtime check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-heroic-crafting.heroic-crafting-actions.Item.omioiKwEf6AFyBBP]{Craft a Project} while engaging in 4 hours or less of exploration activities. It also has space for up to 50 Bulk of crafting materials. Uses the same Vehicle statistics as a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.vehicles.UNOwkQq5lc4cYdZP]{Wagon}.</p>",
